{"parse":{"title":"Sickly Looking Fish","pageid":44855,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|itemid=6299\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_28\n|quality=Common\n|name=Sickly Looking Fish\n|effect=\nUse: Restores 30 health over 15 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.\n|ilvl=5\n|charges=1\n|stack=20\n|sell={{cost|||1}}\n}}</onlyinclude>This fish is caught in the green slime within the Undercity.\n\nNot used in any [[Cooking recipes|cooking recipe]], sickly looking fish has no other value than its health benefits.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6299}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/sickly_looking_fish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}